00123 template<class T> class StackMsgArgMapContainer : public AbstractStackMsgArgMapContainer {
00124     public:
00125         StackMsgArgMapContainer(T *dispatcher = 0, const StackMsgArgMap<T> *arg_map = 0) :  
00126           m_dispatcher(dispatcher), m_arg_map(arg_map) { }
00127 
00128         virtual void Init(T *dispatcher, const StackMsgArgMap<T> *arg_map) {
00129             m_dispatcher = dispatcher;
00130             m_arg_map = arg_map;
00131         } // Init
00132         
00133         virtual BOOLEAN Execute(const StackMsgArgument &arg) const {
00134 //          ASSERT_INFO(m_dispatcher != 0 && m_arg_map != 0, L"StackMsgArgMapContainer not initialized!\n");
00135             ASSERT_ALWAYS(m_dispatcher != 0 && m_arg_map != 0); 
00136             StackMsgArgMap<T>* entry = (StackMsgArgMap<T>*)m_arg_map;
00137             while (entry->arg_id != NoStackMsgArg::ID) {
00138                 ASSERT_ALWAYS(entry->OnArg != 0);
00139                 if (entry->arg_id == arg.Id()) {
00140                     return ((m_dispatcher->*(entry->OnArg))(arg));
00141                 } // if
00142                 entry++;
00143             } // while
00144             return (FALSE);
00145         }   // Execute
00146 
00147     
00148     private:
00149         T *m_dispatcher;
00150         const StackMsgArgMap<T>* m_arg_map;
00151 };
